6:
Ergh... It's just not coming to me! I
need inspiration!
8:
I need some fresh ideas if I'm going
to be able to design some new
outfits...
19:
Hey there, cutie! Got some free
time? I wanna talk with you a little!
23:
I'm Stella. I just finished shopping, so
I've got time.
28:
I'm Karina, nice to meet you! But
anyway, um...
31:
Could I design some clothes for
you?!
39:
Sure am! I'm still in training, but you'll
be seeing my name everywhere
soon enough!
42:
I AM the daughter of the esteemed
Luciana, after all!
45:
Huh, you don't know her? She's
pretty well-known even outside of
the fashion industry...
48:
Mom's famous for her Gilles Couture
designs! Here, check out some of
her work!
56:
I know, right? Only my mom could
come up with designs as sweet as
these!
58:
Mom's got fans all over the world,
and everyone can spot one of her
designs in a heartbeat! I wanna be
like her one day...
62:
Ah, haha... I should calm down a
little, huh? I just get so excited when
talking about this stuff...
70:
...I'm pretty confident with my own
designs, too. I learned a lot since I
was little, always watching my mom
work.
73:
But still! Mom's all like, "It's still too
early for you to get into the industry."
I mean, come on!
77:
No matter how many times I tried to
convince her, she wouldn't change
her stance! So I moved out to prove I
could pull it off!
85:
But... I've just been struggling for
some reason. I keep getting told my
designs are too bizarre, or too
embarrassing to wear!
87:
That's why I've been in a bit of a
slump recently...
91:
But it's really weird! The second I
saw you, all kinds of ideas just came
to me...
94:
Hey, check this one out! I think it's
really cute!
102:
Right? I think this dcollet floral line
would look incredible on you!
109:
I'm worried about the lack of...
coverage.
113:
O-oh, right... It's probably about
twice as revealing as your current
outfit. Maybe more...
117:
A lot of people recommend I wear
outfits like this. I wonder why?
121:
Maybe they think you're the sort of
person who could pull off that sort of
look?
124:
I-I don't mean that in a weird way! I
just get the feeling you could make
any outfit look good...
127:
You're just the cutest, and I think
your beauty could be shown off in
so many different ways by trying on
different things!
129:
I think everyone wants to see your
charm from every angle they can!
133:
...Do you think this would look good
on me?
137:
...Wanna try it on? Let's not overthink
it!
165:
Wait, it's dark out already?! I'm SO
sorry, Stella! I didn't realize!
168: It's okay. I had lots of fun.
172:
...Yeah, me too! I haven't been able
to crank out designs like these in
forever!
175:
Hey, Stella? Do you think I could
come to your house too, sometime?
177:
I love chatting with you, but I also
want to see what kind of
neighborhood you live in!
180:
Those clothes... You didn't get them
from around here, did you? I've
never seen designs or materials like
them!
182:
I have to get familiar with all kinds of
clothing if I'm ever going to catch up
to my mom!
185: So, um. If it's okay! Uh...
196:
Wow. This is insane! What were they
wearing?! I've never seen clothes like
that before!
200:
Welcome to Starview Village, Karina.
I'm happy to have you here.
204:
Thanks, Stella! I'm gonna get
crazy-good at design by being in a
place like this!
207:
In fact, I'm gonna become the best
designer ever! Just you wait and see!
